# UI System

## Component library
- **shadcn/ui** — components live in `src/components/ui/`
- Add via CLI: `npx shadcn@latest add <component>`
- Modify freely — you own the code

## Custom components
- Place in `src/components/` (not in `ui/`)
- Compose from shadcn primitives when possible

## Styling rules
- Use Tailwind classes only
- No inline styles, no CSS modules
- Use `cn()` helper for conditional classes

## Icons
- lucide-react (included with shadcn)